description: Returns the audit history about a specific case if it exists.

parameters.name: caseId
parameters.description: A unique identifier of the case.

parameters.name: domainId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the Cases domain.

nested_items.name: auditEvents
nested_items.description: A list of case audits where each represents a particular edit of the case.

nested_items.name: eventId
nested_items.description: Unique identifier of a case audit history event.

nested_items.name: fields
nested_items.description: A list of Case Audit History event fields.

nested_items.name: eventFieldId
nested_items.description: Unique identifier of field in an Audit History entry.

nested_items.name: booleanValue
nested_items.description: Can be either null, or have a Boolean value type. Only one value can be provided.

nested_items.name: doubleValue
nested_items.description: Can be either null, or have a Double value type. Only one value can be provided.

nested_items.name: emptyValue
nested_items.description: An empty value. You cannot set EmptyFieldValue on a field that is required on a case template.

nested_items.name: stringValue
nested_items.description: Can be either null, or have a String value type. Only one value can be provided.

nested_items.name: userArnValue
nested_items.description: Can be either null, or have a String value type formatted as an ARN. Only one value can be provided.

nested_items.name: booleanValue
nested_items.description: Can be either null, or have a Boolean value type. Only one value can be provided.

nested_items.name: doubleValue
nested_items.description: Can be either null, or have a Double value type. Only one value can be provided.

nested_items.name: emptyValue
nested_items.description: An empty value. You cannot set EmptyFieldValue on a field that is required on a case template.

nested_items.name: stringValue
nested_items.description: Can be either null, or have a String value type. Only one value can be provided.

nested_items.name: userArnValue
nested_items.description: Can be either null, or have a String value type formatted as an ARN. Only one value can be provided.

nested_items.name: performedBy
nested_items.description: Information of the user which performed the audit.

nested_items.name: iamPrincipalArn
nested_items.description: Unique identifier of an IAM role.

nested_items.name: customEntity
nested_items.description: Any provided entity.

nested_items.name: userArn
nested_items.description: Represents the Amazon Connect ARN of the user.

nested_items.name: performedTime
nested_items.description: Time at which an Audit History event took place.

nested_items.name: relatedItemType
nested_items.description: The Type of the related item.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The Type of an audit history event.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results. This is null if there are no more results to return.
